groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Cars, We got cars...3rd try
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description: This one is located near the other one but I think I have moved it to a more muggle free area. The theme is cars for reasons that are clear when you get to the area. I have noticed the changes across the street depending on the economy. This one is a small L&L container. Be sure to read the parking signs. Better on w/e or evenings
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:encoded_hints: on the CAR side of fence

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: I think the hardest part of this one was finding a place to park. Otherwise a quick find. TFTC
